The paper deals with sequence prediction, which is a problem in information theory (cs.IT) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The paper also discusses the existence of predictors for arbitrary families of stochastic processes, which could fall under the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS) or systems and control (cs.SI).
